  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators want to know whether the intravenous ascorbic acid would reduce the blood
      loss during laparoscopic myoma surgery. The investigators randomized patients into
      intravenous ascorbic acid group and placebo group and examined the blood loss in both groups.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
