  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  uterine myoma

          -  be planning to laparoscopic myomectomy

          -  images ; the number of myoma &lt;4

          -  images ; the diameter of the largest myoma &lt;9cm

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  be planning other surgery in addition to laparoscopy

          -  clinically significant coagulation abnormality
      </textblock>
